        "lang": "chs",
        "text": "那时，王正与上帝仆人的侍者基哈西谈话，让基哈西把以利沙所做的一切大事讲给他听。"
      },
      "cnv": {
        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "那時王正在和神人的僕人基哈西交談，說：“請你向我講述以利沙所作的一切大事。”"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "那時王正與神人的僕人基哈西說：「請你將以利沙所行的一切大事告訴我。」"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Now the king was talking with Gehazi, the servant of the man of God, saying, “Please relate to me all the great things that Elisha has done.”"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "The king was talking to Gehazi, the servant of the man of God, and had said, “Tell me about all the great things Elisha has done.”"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "As she came in, the king was talking with Gehazi, the servant of the man of God. The king had just said, “Tell me some stories about the great things Elisha has done.”"
      }
